text: te puokke bercha brachheang( nung batobanhchea) . dau che neah yeung ka banhchoun tukchomnn del haur khlang towkean puokke( thveu aoy bak tomnb ning khauch chamkar) . haey yeung ban phlasabdaur chamkar teangpir robsa puokke tow chea chamkar del mean phle rosacheate lving ning roukkhcheate kmean phle ning meante daem pou ttrea techtuoch tebonnaoh
